                </div>
                <div class="testi-info">
                    <div class="icon">
                        <i class="fa fa-user-circle-o"></i>
                        <h3>Ivanka<span>Blagoevgrad</span></h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                <div class="testi-details">
                    <p>This is the best hospital in Sofia. The doctors are very professional and kind.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="testi-info">
                    <div class="icon">
                        <i class="fa fa-user-circle-o"></i>
                        <h3>Dobri Ivanov<span>Sofia</span></h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
